---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Japonica · Our process" description="How we work together — six steps from your first enquiry to your wedding day, with Japonica." >
<header class="page-header">
  <div class="crumb"><span class="lspc lspc-32">Japonica · How we work together</span></div>
  <h1>Our process</h1>
  <p class="subline">Six steps from your first message to the day itself. We are here through all of them.</p>
</header>

<section class="steps-wrap">

  <div class="step-row reveal">
    <div class="step-num">01</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2>Fill out our enquiry form</h2>
      <p>The most important step. This helps us get a picture of your floral dreams and confirms we have availability for your date.</p>
      <p>The more details the better. Do not be afraid to over-share.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step-row reveal">
    <div class="step-num">02</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2>Wait for our reply</h2>
      <p>With everything you have shared, we work on a customised quote. If we need a few more details we will be in touch.</p>
      <p>Check your junk folder in case your quote is hiding there. Our terms and conditions are sent with your quote.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step-row reveal">
    <div class="step-num">03</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2>Accept the quote</h2>
      <p>Like what you see? Lock us in. It is officially locked once your deposit is paid.</p>
      <p>Before securing your date we can organise a phone consultation for any questions you may have. Do not stress on the finer details yet. We have plenty of time to refine and plan together.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step-row reveal">
    <div class="step-num">04</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2>You're booked</h2>
      <p>Once your deposit lands, you are in. Sit back, relax, let the fun part begin.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step-row reveal">
    <div class="step-num">05</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2>Consultation</h2>
      <p>As we get closer to your date we organise a time to meet either in person or by video. We talk through your order details and all the fun final details: colours, flower preferences, timings.</p>
      <p>These meetings happen four to eight weeks out from your wedding, so more of the day is confirmed by then.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="step-row reveal">
    <div class="step-num">06</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2>Final confirmations</h2>
      <p>The countdown is on. Two weeks out we touch base to confirm any small final changes. Once final confirmations are done, the final balance is due.</p>
      <p>Then we get to work and you get to look forward to walking into a room you have chosen, full of flowers that look like you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<section class="closer-section">
  <div class="closer">
    <h2 class="reveal">Ready to start?</h2>
    <a href="/enquire/" class="cta reveal"><span class="lspc lspc-36">Begin a conversation</span></a>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.65; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow-x: hidden; }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }

  .lspc { display: inline-block; }
  .lspc-22 { letter-spacing: 0.22em; margin-right: -0.22em; }
  .lspc-28 { letter-spacing: 0.28em; margin-right: -0.28em; }
  .lspc-32 { letter-spacing: 0.32em; margin-right: -0.32em; }
  .lspc-34 { letter-spacing: 0.34em; margin-right: -0.34em; }
  .lspc-36 { letter-spacing: 0.36em; margin-right: -0.36em; }

  nav.top { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 22px 56px; background: rgba(239, 233, 220, 0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(6px); color: var(--ink); border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(53, 42, 53, 0.08); }
  nav.top .mark { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 20px; }
  nav.top .links { display: flex; gap: 36px; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; }
  nav.top .links a { transition: opacity 0.3s; }
  nav.top .links a:hover { opacity: 0.55; }

  .page-header { padding: 160px 56px 80px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-header .crumb { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--stone); margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .page-header h1 { font-family: var(--display); font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .page-header .subline { font-size: 17px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.7; }

  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 1.1s ease-out, transform 1.1s ease-out; }
  .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  .steps-wrap { padding: 80px 56px 140px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .step-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: 56px; padding: 48px 0; border-top: 0.5px solid rgba(53, 42, 53, 0.12); align-items: start; }
  .step-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(53, 42, 53, 0.12); }
  .step-num { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 80px; color: var(--stone); line-height: 1; }
  .step-content h2 { font-family: var(--display); font-size: clamp(28px, 3.4vw, 40px); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 18px; color: var(--ink); }
  .step-content p { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 640px; }
  .step-content p + p { margin-top: 14px; }

  .closer-section { padding: 96px 56px 180px; text-align: center; }
  .closer h2 { font-family: var(--display); font-size: clamp(30px, 4.4vw, 52px); line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 48px; font-weight: 400; }
  .cta { display: inline-block; background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); padding: 20px 60px; border-radius: var(--radius); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; transition: background 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease; }
  .cta:hover { background: #241A24; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  footer { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); padding: 96px 56px 48px; }
  .foot-top { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto 72px; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 48px; border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(239, 233, 220, 0.15); }
  .foot-mark { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 44px; margin-bottom: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; padding-left: 0.18em; display: inline-block; }
  .foot-philo { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.7; line-height: 1.7; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .foot-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 56px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .foot-col { text-align: center; }
  .foot-h { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.55; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .foot-line { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.9; opacity: 0.88; display: block; }
  .foot-line:hover { opacity: 0.6; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
  .foot-meta { max-width: 1400px; margin: 80px auto 0; padding-top: 32px; border-top: 0.5px solid rgba(239, 233, 220, 0.15); display: flex; flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 10px 28px; text-align: center; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.5; }
  .foot-meta a { border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(239, 233, 220, 0.3); padding-bottom: 1px; }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    nav.top { padding: 14px 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; row-gap: 8px; }
    nav.top .mark { font-size: 17px; }
    nav.top .links { width: 100%; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; font-size: 10px; }
    nav.top .links .lspc-28 { letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-right: -0.08em; }
    .page-header { padding: 120px 24px 56px; }
    .steps-wrap { padding: 48px 24px 96px; }
    .step-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; padding: 36px 0; }
    .step-num { font-size: 56px; }
    .closer-section { padding: 64px 24px 96px; }
    .foot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .foot-mark { font-size: 34px; }
    footer { padding: 64px 24px 32px; }
    .foot-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; font-size: 12px; } .foot-line { font-size: 15px; } .foot-h { font-size: 11px; }
  }
</style>
